\newlabel{fig:ratio}{{5}{8}{Ratio IPR$_{\rm trib}$ / IPR$_{\rm fib}$ at $T=50$ as a function of $\lambda $. The ratio increases to $\sim 8.6$ at $\lambda =1.5$ before declining at large coupling.\relax }{figure.caption.9}{}}
